Cross-platform open-world ARPG Wuthering Waves is out on PlayStation 5.

In this adventure, you wake up as "Rover," joined by a vibrant cast of Resonators. Immerse yourself in the unfolding world as you dive into exhilarating combat and explore a vast landscape with unprecedented freedom.

Mark your calendars for October 9th (UTC+8) as Version 2.7 "Dawn Breaks on Dark Tides" is set to arrive. Experience the thrilling finale of Rinascita! 

New 5-Star Resonators Galbrena and Qiuyuan will be introduced as the story unfolds, along with fresh Main Quests, new areas to discover, and a wealth of exciting special events. 

Stay tuned to our official social media channels for the latest updates!
